{"tid":1467960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(關於機場)所有手足入一入","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:12:55.000Z","uid":42286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e4aa660b9b419bc94a6436f200bd99f2e509ea6d","tid":1467960,"uid":42286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:46:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">請記住核彈都唔割</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武死守被捕係犧牲而唔係送頭<br />\n和理非只想靜坐係信念唔係左膠</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n人無完人，每個人都會做錯，更何況係一大班人？<br />\n812大家被fake news誤導，係有屌但無人割<br />\n813打錯人，唔打都打咗，希望大家都係屌完但唔割<br />\n呢一刻最重要嘅係點樣繼續打場仗<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對家會包裝 我哋都要識包裝</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">今日捉到公安，白色恐怖，狗衝入機場同拔真槍<br />\n仲要由612開始<br />\n6個手足捨身取義<br />\n200萬人上街<br />\n到721元朗事件<br />\n對居民使用摧淚彈<br />\n811一個女仔被狗射盲 葵芳地鐵站放摧淚彈 太古站近距離headshot加扶手電梯推人再濫用武力<br />\n幾百手足被捕同被政治檢控<br />\n懷疑中共公安混入執法部門<br />\n未能盡錄</span><br />\n完全可以合理化手足受到驚嚇先會未fact check就打人，仲可以推返個責任俾狗同政府<br />\n<br />\n聽日814機場麻煩文宣組做下宣傳圖，手足們(無分和理非同勇武)我哋一齊同記者朋友救護朋友道歉<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">我哋叻過狗嘅地方係我哋做錯係會道歉</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n之後要再打人捉狗嘅可以<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但一完要FACT CHECK</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但一完要FACT CHECK</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但一完要FACT CHECK</span></span></strong><br />\nCHECK到係狗 勇武少少咪私了 和平非暴力咪搵個狗牌(<strong>香港幫狗隻打晶片會有隻狗個名同主人電話號碼</strong>)戴下再綁大堂示眾 話俾全世界知香港政府同狗要用卧底(連登仔model answer:why not both?)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">如果係蟲仲可以話俾全世界(尤其美國)知中共已經插手香港示威，到時會點大家都知道啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力，唔係要大家用自己嘅標準去逼其他人行自己條路，鄧小平都有講不論白貓黑貓 捉到老鼠就係好貓，大家唔好再犯同樣錯誤，當俾阿寶抖下好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後希望大家早日到獅子山山頂"},{"pid":"f93cc37ed57312621e41216d34391c53894e1b8e","tid":1467960,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:46:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b943c6acfa04388983fc76796985ff9dd738af","tid":1467960,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:20.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n【跪求大家入黎睇下，我好想香港贏】關於鬼關於衝動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466732</a>"},{"pid":"dc4c4430df09c1025764ce7243b6e4a01bbc8ae5","tid":1467960,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:36.000Z","msg":"機場三不<br />\n不衝突 不打人 不入禁區"},{"pid":"be496c4d36c02bd299de855f4b5cb30227c3e81f","tid":1467960,"uid":94538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:38.000Z","msg":"814照入機場，但和理非主場，道歉+幫旅客+文宣！<br />\n<br />\n[推！！！ 道歉是必須] 話錯既係政府，洗乜撚野道歉既入<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467612</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a99f4baee015d08646c0a8dccc129afde8e19529","tid":1467960,"uid":42286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:16.000Z","msg":"我知我寫得唔算好 但希望大家幫手推上去 至少少一個3毛post"},{"pid":"f647a773fb9472eeb0240ccea2f63aebe9e3ec93","tid":1467960,"uid":42286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"aa250a55c37e52669895771a9df547cce474b4ae","tid":1467960,"uid":42286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e4f01271dd9416bdd50205a2ae4e21f5e185f16d","tid":1467960,"uid":42286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9d9931a2584fc1e17b9d5fcf20f76975f1cb8359","tid":1467960,"uid":65556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:00:09.000Z","msg":"各有各做<br />\n點都唔會割"},{"pid":"b3882ba2f4f2964377d8d039d99c8e10b7e36292","tid":1467960,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:03:06.000Z","msg":"中間酒紅色既字好難睇🙇🏻&zwj;♂️🙇🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"ffb1428558a033223b2013be6c35027c93acd4f1","tid":1467960,"uid":42286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3882ba2f4f2964377d8d039d99c8e10b7e36292","tid":1467960,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:03:06.000Z","msg":"中間酒紅色既字好難睇🙇🏻&zwj;♂️🙇🏻&zwj;♂️"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:12.000Z","msg":"平時都做CD-ROM 下次會改<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n酒紅色都係講大家呢兩個月所見所聞 大家應該唔會忘記"},{"pid":"7b170da5173f16b07b6fa0a0a84660c304736666","tid":1467960,"uid":42286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3ac45198856ae806aaf7ba578c0b3d55ffb39b5b","tid":1467960,"ui